ed\nstartups but they serves as a great example of what to communicate when looking\nfor talent that gets offered "},{"children":[{"children":[],"type":"text","value":"exciting"}],"tagName":"em","properties":{},"type":"element"},{"children":[],"type":"text","value":" and "},{"children":[{"children":[],"type":"text","value":"once-in-a-lifetime"}],"tagName":"em","properties":{},"type":"element"},{"children":[],"type":"text","value":" opportunities\nevery day."}],"tagName":"p","properties":{},"type":"element"},{"children":[],"type":"text","value":"\n"},{"children":[{"children":[],"type":"text","value":"If you have an established tech team already, let them write a blog. This will\nhelp in proving that you are up to your promises and also gives an insight into\nyour daily work. Good examples‚Äìfrom around‚Äìare "},{"children":[{"children":[],"type":"text","value":"Vaamo"}],"tagName":"a","properties":{"href":"http://codecraft.vaamo.de/","target":"_blank","rel":["nofollow","noreferrer"]},"type":"element"},{"children":[],"type":"text","value":" or "},{"children":[{"children":[],"type":"text","value":"flinc"}],"tagName":"a","properties":{"href":"http://blog.flinc.org/devblog/","target":"_blank","rel":["nofollow","noreferrer"]},"type":"element"},{"children":[],"type":"text","value":"."}],"tagName":"p","properties":{},"type":"element"},{"children":[],"type":"text","value":"\n"},{"children":[{"children":[{"children":[{"children":[],"tagName":"path","properties":{"fillRule":"evenodd","d":"M4 9h1v1H4c-1.5 0-3-1.69-3-3.5S2.55 3 4 3h4c1.45 0 3 1.69 3 3.5 0 1.41-.91 2.72-2 3.25V8.59c.58-.45 1-1.27 1-2.09C10 5.22 8.98 4 8 4H4c-.98 0-2 1.22-2 2.5S3 9 4 9zm9-3h-1v1h1c1 0 2 1.22 2 2.5S13.98 12 13 12H9c-.98 0-2-1.22-2-2.5 0-.83.42-1.64 1-2.09V6.25c-1.09.53-2 1.84-2 3.25C6 11.31 7.55 13 9 13h4c1.45 0 3-1.69 3-3.5S14.5 6 13 6z"},"type":"element"}],"tagName":"svg","properties":{"ariaHidden":"true","focusable":"false","height":"16","version":"1.1","viewBox":"0 0 16 16","width":"16"},"type":